
Intro
=====

Scopira is a C++ software development library that provides facilities for high performance
numerical computing, visual application developement (2D and 3D) and parallel processing.
Scopira may be used for a wide variety of scientific and engineering data analysis
and visualization applications.

See http://demko.ca/scopira/ for more info.

